name: We Made You
wikiSummary: "We Made You" is the first official single by American rapper Eminem from his album Relapse. The song features Charmagne Tripp. It is Eminem's second official solo single in 4 years. The single, produced by him, was released on April 7, 2009 along with a music video. According to the We Made You Songfacts Connecticut producer Doc Ish supplied the beat including soul singer Charmagne Tripp's hook.
